text: Robert Hungerford may refer to: *Robert Hungerford, 2nd Baron Hungerford (1409–1459), the second but eldest surviving son of Walter, lord Hungerford, served in the French wars *Robert Hungerford, 3rd Baron Hungerford (1431–1464), supported the Lancastrians cause the War of the Roses *Robert Hungerford (MP for Calne), in 1553, MP for Calne (UK Parliament constituency)
title: Robert Hungerford
